            "date_published": "2024-10-14T09:12:15.289Z",
            "content_html": "<img src=\"../images/chunking-express.jpg\" alt=\"chunking-express\" style=\"zoom: 10%;\" />\n\n<p>“不知道從什麽時候開始，在每個東西上都有一個日期。秋刀魚會過期，肉醬會過期，連保鮮紙都會過期，我開始懷疑在這個世界上還有什麽東西是不會過期的？”</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h1 id=\"序言\"><a href=\"#序言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"序言\"></a>序言</h1><p>这是一个对于新的github博客的测试文档。</p>\n<p>由于原先的博客近三年来缺乏维护，导致难以部署，只能使用旧版<code>node.js-12.4.0</code>进行部署，还状况频出，故放弃。</p>\n<p>原博客链接为：<a href=\"https://we1005.junyan.art/\">他的国 (junyan.art)</a></p>\n<p>现采用最新的<code>node.js-20.18.0</code>进行建站，但愿能继续长久维护下去。</p>\n<h2 id=\"引用测试\"><a href=\"#引用测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引用测试\"></a>引用测试</h2><blockquote>\n<p>虞美人·听雨</p>\n<p>【宋】蒋捷</p>\n<p>少年听雨歌楼上，红烛昏罗帐。</p>\n<p>壮年听雨客舟中，江阔云低、断雁叫西风。</p>\n<p>而今听雨僧庐下，鬓已星星也。</p>\n<p>悲欢离合总无情，一任阶前、点滴到天明。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"超链接测试\"><a href=\"#超链接测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"超链接测试\"></a>超链接测试</h2><p><a href=\"https://we1005.junyan.art/posts/cfa2b402.html\">当代中国的三大社会思潮 | 他的国 (junyan.art)</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"代码测试\"><a href=\"#代码测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码测试\"></a>代码测试</h2><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">double</span>&amp; <span class=\"title\">lala</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">double</span> arg[])</span><span class=\"comment\">//返回一个引用类型</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">double</span>&amp; a = arg[<span class=\"number\">1</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> a;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">double</span> d_array[<span class=\"number\">3</span>] = &#123; <span class=\"number\">0.00</span>,<span class=\"number\">1.23</span>,<span class=\"number\">3.36</span> &#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">double</span>&amp; qq = <span class=\"built_in\">lala</span>(d_array);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    qq = <span class=\"number\">5.42</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    cout &lt;&lt; d_array[<span class=\"number\">1</span>] &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"自定义html代码测试\"><a href=\"#自定义html代码测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自定义html代码测试\"></a>自定义html代码测试</h2><iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=\"410\" height=\"110\" src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=40729148&auto=0&height=66\"></iframe>",
